node.text:
Nothing better than watching redfish blowup on a topwater!
.
The action was non stop today with @mariah_970 and @chasinactioncharters, we caught so many fish! 
.

Epic day!!
 
Hat- @brittapparel

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝓑𝓻𝓲𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓷𝔂 𝓞𝓼𝓴𝓮𝔂 in Sarasota, Florida with @chasinactioncharters, and @brittapparel. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Did you know the color of the water affects the color of redfish? The more brackish the water is, the more golden the fish is! If you catch them closer to the beach, they're lighter! @chasinactioncharters 
.
Hat @brittapparel

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝓑𝓻𝓲𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓷𝔂 𝓞𝓼𝓴𝓮𝔂 in Boca Grande, Florida with @hooters. May be an image of 1 person and nature.

node.text:
Thinking about how I'm going to order wings and fried pickles when I get off the boat! I love the convenience of having my food delivered to the house, especially after a long day on the boat.
.

node.text:
As we head into Labor Day weekend, we want to remind everyone how important it is to stay safe on the water. 
.
We have teamed up with the @uscg @ridedrydrivedry campaign. Please help us in this campaign by reposting and sharing our video.  Thanks, and stay safe !! @chasinactioncharters

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝓑𝓻𝓲𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓷𝔂 𝓞𝓼𝓴𝓮𝔂 in Sarasota, Florida. May be an image of 1 person, dog and outdoors.

node.text:
Her wings were ready, but our hearts were not! 🐕 🌈
.
.
Saying goodbye to my best friend after almost 13 years is the hardest thing I ever had to do. This past week and a half has been so hard watching her slowly get sicker and weaker. 
After talking to the vet,we knew the time had come to say goodbye to our girl ! 
.
Goodbyes are not forever
Goodbyes are not the end
They simply mean 
I’ll miss you until we meet again 
Rip Jewels! 
You will be missed more than you know! ❤️
